Title: check_traceroute: Report correct number of hops
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1683714747
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

The active check <tt>check_traceroute</tt>, configurable via the ruleset <i>Check current routing</i>,
always reported one hop too many when outputting the number of hops. This affected both the textual
result and the recorded metric.
